00:48:22,085 --> 00:48:26,847
while we do the work behind the scenes to ensure the experience remains seamless and consistent.

455
00:48:29,367 --> 00:48:33,068
Now one of the main challenges from a music point of view was concerning how we could

456
00:48:33,168 --> 00:48:36,829
preserve the integrity of the original tracks, as James has just mentioned.

