00:49:59,408 --> 00:50:01,129
gave them something to build to.

482
00:50:02,950 --> 00:50:05,111
As such, they also needed a standard structure,

483
00:50:05,151 --> 00:50:07,091
so you couldn't really have a nine-minute epic,

484
00:50:07,211 --> 00:50:10,533
prog, kind of solo or anything like that.

