00:51:01,815 --> 00:51:04,937
often a hurdle for some of the older catalog. And as

496
00:51:04,977 --> 00:51:08,979
Jay mentioned, these are the songs complete with vocals, and for a family

497
00:51:09,039 --> 00:51:12,261
friendly game, we needed them to be lyrically suitable for the rating.

